          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/849_step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> and <strong>cayenne pepper</strong>&nbsp;to a large bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and mix it up</p>\r\n<p>Crack the <strong>egg<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into a shallow bowl</p>\r\n<p>Add 3 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [6 tbsp]</span><strong> flour</strong> to another plate</p>\r\n<p>Place all of the <strong>prawns</strong> in the <strong>flour</strong> (tap off any excess), add them to the beaten <strong>egg</strong>, then put them all into the bowl of <strong>panko</strong> and&nbsp;give them a good old mix up until they're coated</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/849.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
