            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/849.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Strip the<strong> mint leaves</strong> from their stems and set aside them aside</p>\r\n<p>Slice the remaining <strong>shallot</strong> finely</p>\r\n<p>Return the pot to a medium heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong></p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the sliced&nbsp;<strong>shallot</strong>&nbsp;and cook over a medium-low heat for 4 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 5,
